on exitFrame me
  [  0] pusharglistnoret 0 ...................... <>
  [  2] extcall 1 ............................... nextframe()
  [  4] pusharglist 0 ........................... <>
  [  6] thebuiltin 2 ............................ <the frame>
  [  8] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <the frame>
  [ 10] extcall 3 ............................... go(the frame)
  [ 12] ret
end
